name: People - Avatars + Realistic Names
description:
A component library of not only beautiful avatars, but realistic names that were consciously created to try and best match their ethnicity & culture. No need to think of names anymore to match faces when creating mockups. Simply choose from the variants male or female for sex type, square or round for shape, and the person by name.


This collection of 150 avatars was curated from many talented creators on Unsplash.


I hope all of you find this useful & time saving!
